#. <CLT 04>ネズミー城に着いた。<CLT>
msgctxt "0001"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Here we are at the dining hall...\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>ここは、島全体が遊園地になっているらしい。<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>色々と突っ込んではいけない感じのデザインだ…<CLT>
msgctxt "0002"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>This is the one place where we all spend a lot of time\n"
"together.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>俺たちの他に人影はないみたいだけど…<CLT>
#. <CLT 04>さてどうしようか？<CLT>
msgctxt "0003"
msgid "For breakfast, Japanese style is best."
msgstr ""

#. メリーゴーランドに乗ろう
msgctxt "0004"
msgid ""
"You got it! All I need is my miso soup and my pickled\n"
"veggies and I'm good to go!"
msgstr ""

#. メリーゴーランドはいいよね！
#. 子供のころからあれが一番好きだよ。
msgctxt "0005"
msgid ""
"But still, that doesn't mean I *never* eat Western\n"
"food."
msgstr ""

#. だってボクが安心して乗れる
#. 数少ない乗り物のひとつだからね。
msgctxt "0006"
msgid ""
"Sometimes I eat toast for lunch! All I need is my\n"
"fried egg and my banana and I'm good to go!"
msgstr ""

#. あの危機感のかけらもない、のんびりとした
#. 上下と回転には、心癒されるよ…
msgctxt "0007"
msgid ""
"But either way, breakfast is the most important meal\n"
"of the day. Make sure you eat plenty, Makoto!"
msgstr ""

#. それに、爆発でもしないかぎり、
#. 命の危険はなさそうだしね！
msgctxt "0008"
msgid "Want something to drink?"
msgstr ""

#. よし、さっそく行こうよ！
#. やっぱりここで乗るならネズミだよね！
msgctxt "0009"
msgid "...Is that why you brought me here?"
msgstr ""

#. お化け屋敷に入ろう
msgctxt "0010"
msgid ""
"I thought maybe you had something important you wanted\n"
"to talk about."
msgstr ""

#. お化け屋敷か…
#. いまいち楽しみ方がわからないんだよね。
msgctxt "0011"
msgid ""
"But thank you for your thoughtfulness! Okay then,\n"
"let's have some tea!"
msgstr ""

#. びっくりしすぎて笑っちゃうこととかはあるから
#. 楽しくないってわけではないんだろうけど…
msgctxt "0012"
msgid "When I'm starving, it's burger time!"
msgstr ""

#. 恐怖なら、わざわざお化け屋敷に入らなくても
#. 日常的に感じられるしね！
msgctxt "0013"
msgid "I won't deny your preference, but..."
msgstr ""

#. …あ、でも実は本物の死体が混じってて、
#. 運悪く見つけちゃう…とかは嫌だなぁ。
msgctxt "0014"
msgid ""
"...hamburgers are utterly unorthodox! A true Japanese\n"
"student should always recommend rice balls!"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>どういう心配の仕方だよ…<CLT>
msgctxt "0015"
msgid ""
"It's true, hamburgers do provide plenty of caloric\n"
"energy, but they're bad for your digestive system!"
msgstr ""

#. ジェットコースターに乗ろう！
msgctxt "0016"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Hmm... What to do...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. …うん、その気持ちはよくわかるよ。
#. こういうところに来たら、普通は乗るよね。
msgctxt "0017"
msgid "So what do you like to do at night?"
msgstr ""

#. でも…わかるだろう？
#. あれは事故率ナンバーワンの乗り物だって…
msgctxt "0018"
msgid ""
"After I study for the next day's lesson, I like to\n"
"cleanse body and soul, strip down, then hit the sack!"
msgstr ""

#. ボクと一緒に乗るのだけはオススメしないよ…
#. 生きてここから帰りたければね。
msgctxt "0019"
msgid ""
"You should follow the same regimen! Even outside of\n"
"class, students have no time for goofing off!"
msgstr ""

#. 迷いそうだな
msgctxt "0020"
msgid "How do you get your hair to do that?"
msgstr ""

#. あ、そうだね！
#. ボクが一緒だし、間違いなく迷うと思うよ！
msgctxt "0021"
msgid ""
"To do what? Hair doesn't matter! Your only duty is to\n"
"study!"
msgstr ""

#. サバイバル中サバイバルなんて…
#. なかなかないレアな展開じゃないかな！
msgctxt "0022"
msgid ""
"Everyone here lacks the necessary qualities of a\n"
"student! And that includes you, Makoto!"
msgstr ""

#. ふふふ…
#. 無事に出てこられるといいね！
msgctxt "0023"
msgid "You think that clock is right?"
msgstr ""

#. <CLT 04>なんでそんなに嬉しそうなんだ…<CLT>
msgctxt "0024"
msgid "Hrmm... According to my watch..."
msgstr ""

#. 楽しそうだな
msgctxt "0025"
msgid "M-My goodness! It's slightly off!"
msgstr ""

#. そうだね。
#. なんだか、子供の頃を思い出すよ。
msgctxt "0026"
msgid ""
"When the clock everyone relies on is off, that's a big\n"
"problem..."
msgstr ""

#. …とは言っても、小さい頃にたった一度
#. 両親と行ったことがあるってだけなんだけどね。
msgctxt "0027"
msgid ""
"But who can we ask to fix it? It'd probably have to\n"
"be...Monokuma, right?"
msgstr ""

#. なんとなく、こんなところにくる機会なんて
#. ないと思ってたからさ…
msgctxt "0028"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Hmm... What to do...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. 今日はキミと一緒に来れて、すごくうれしいよ。
msgctxt "0029"
msgid "What should we talk about...?"
msgstr ""

#. 疲れそうだな
msgctxt "0030"
msgid ""
"What *is* there to talk about? If you don't know what\n"
"else to do with yourself..."
msgstr ""

#. うん…
#. ボクもそんなに体力ある方じゃないからさ…
msgctxt "0031"
msgid ""
"...you should review the school regulations in detail\n"
"one more time!"
msgstr ""

#. 一日で全制覇とかは、さすがにちょっと無理かな…
msgctxt "0032"
msgid ""
"It's important for every student to know their\n"
"school's regulations like the back of their hand!"
msgstr ""

#. …って、ああそうか、そうだよね！
#. ボクと一緒だから疲れるって意味だよね！
msgctxt "0033"
msgid "You're always so...fired up."
msgstr ""

#. よし、食べ歩きだ
msgctxt "0034"
msgid "Now I have to hear that from you, too?"
msgstr ""

#. え…？
#. ボクとかい…？
msgctxt "0035"
msgid ""
"I mean...other classmates have told me the\n"
"same thing before."
msgstr ""

#. うーん…それはたぶん、
#. ボク以外の人とやった方が楽しいと思うよ。
msgctxt "0036"
msgid ""
"Honestly, I never really understood what any of them\n"
"were talking about."
msgstr ""

#. まぁ、キミの雄姿を見てるだけでいいなら
#. ボクにもできそうだけど…
msgctxt "0037"
msgid ""
"All I know is, I don't want to get dragged down by\n"
"those around me!"
msgstr ""

#. あの城に登ろう
msgctxt "0038"
msgid "So no matter what anyone says, I will not falter!"
msgstr ""

#. あ、それはいい考えだね！
#. あそこからなら島全体が見渡せそうだし。
msgctxt "0039"
msgid "Hahahahaha! Do you know what I'm talking about!?"
msgstr ""

#. ああでも、ボクと一緒に高いところに行くときは
#. 十分注意してね。
msgctxt "0040"
msgid "Do you know how to cook?"
msgstr ""

#. 特に、手すり的な物には絶対に
#. 寄りかからない方がいいよ！
msgctxt "0041"
msgid ""
"Of course! I've been very diligent in my culinary\n"
"studies."
msgstr ""

#. じゃあ、早速行ってみようか！
msgctxt "0042"
msgid ""
"My personal specialties are rice balls, and rice with\n"
"green tea."
msgstr ""

#. やっぱり帰るか…
msgctxt "0043"
msgid ""
"I've been learning how to make my rice balls in\n"
"different shapes. The star shape is the hardest!"
msgstr ""

#. え…せっかく来たのにかい？
msgctxt "0044"
msgid ""
"See? Even I know how to relax and have a good time\n"
"once in a while! Hahaha!"
msgstr ""

#. こういうところは久しぶりだから、
#. 少し覗いてみたかったんだけどな…
msgctxt "0045"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>His idea of a \"good time\" is kinda...weird.\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""

#. キミがどうしてもっていうならそうするけど…
#. …残念だな。
msgctxt "0046"
msgid ""
"<CLT 4>Hmm... What to do...?\n"
"<CLT>"
msgstr ""
